This is a loacl Phonebook web application.
Each record includes name and phone, the phonBookRecord & phonBookSchema Obj can be modified easily for other attributes.
You can add, edit, delete and search [by name or phone].


running the app :
First go to Config/serverConf.js and update:
	'HOME_PATH': path from home to project dir
	'PORT': local port to run the app
    'DB_PATH' : db url path for example 'mongodb://localhost/myphonebook'

After initilazing the configuration above , run:
npm run app
